# Health Check Flow
# Simple health check to verify API is running

@name "API Health Check"

## Check server health
GET {{BASE_URL}}/health
@assert status == 200
@assert body.status == "healthy"
@assert headers.content-type contains "application/json"

## Check server info
GET {{BASE_URL}}/info
@assert status == 200
@assert body.version exists
@assert body.environment exists
@capture version body.version